                                        boolean callSuperMethod)
Add a concrete method invoking the interceptor interceptorName with the same parameters,name,return type as the method method

Parameters:
concreteClass - the concrete where to add the interceptor method
method - method from which is generating the new proxy method
interceptorName - the interceptor name implementing the interface InvocationHandler. This name must be the name of an existing field of the concrete class
callSuperMethod - if true the concrete implementation of the method will call super()
